dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ronald Collins. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Andrea Ross.
Thank you, Andrea. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five eight two four six and my date of birth is one two zero six eight.
Thank you for that information, Andrea. I also need your current address for our records. Could you please provide me with your street address, city, and postal code?
Of course, my address is 123 Maple Street, Oakville, postal code L6J 2W1.
Thank you for providing your address. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Andrea?
No, that's all for now, thank you.
Thank you for your time, Andrea. If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
